lead_paragraph: Katie Ledecky won the 800-meter freestyle by nearly 15 seconds at the Arena Pro Swim meet Saturday night, her third victory in three days just over two months before the U.S. Olympic swimming trials.

headline.main: Ledecky and Phelps Swim to Victories in Arizona
